com.bitwise.decaf.editor
Interface Type

All Superinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
Type.NoType
public interface Type
extends Comparable, com.bitwise.decaf.editor.Configurable, Grammar.ClassReference

A Decaf UI representation of a class. All types are representatives of a GType, available with typeSource(). A type may bear details, i.e., documentation provided by the configuration file, which specified a display name, and optionally a discussion of the content and purpose of the type.
